grant TruongPhong to NV404;
grant TruongPhong to NV406;
grant TruongPhong to NV502;
grant TruongPhong to NV504;
grant TruongPhong to NV506;

-- Them cac nhan vien giu vai tro Truong du an vao role TruongDuAn
